data.title: South Correctional Entity
data.text:
South Correctional Entity (SCORE Jail) is a government agency pursuant to RCW 39.34.030(3) in Des Moines, Washington. SCORE is owned by the Cities of : Auburn, Burien, Des Moines, Renton, SeaTac, and Tukwila.

MISSION

To provide the highest quality public safety services to those we serve.

VISION

Dedicated to creating an environment of public trust and excellence through all layers of services. Enhancing the field of corrections with integrity, innovation, and commitment.

VALUES

Service: We serve and are responsible to the public. We seek their trust and invite their involvement.

Excellence: We are committed to seeking excellence through the highest levels of professionalism, courage, and honor.

Respect: We respect each otherâ€™s differences and treat others with courtesy, dignity, and consideration.

Collaboration: We work with our stakeholders as partners, to support mutual ideas and goals.
